Mice C57BL/6 mice were purchased from The Jackson Laboratories (Bar Harbor, ME) at 6±7 weeks of age. Mice were housed locally in microisolator cages and were used within 7 days of receipt. None were found to have preexisting anti-MHV antibodies prior to use. Mice were inoculated intracranially (ic) with 1 ϫ 10 5 plaque-forming units (PFU) of virus in 30 l of Dulbecco's phosphatebuffered saline (DPBS). 


